{"tid":830750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭指香港因高鐵進入「幸福時代」 相信市民會歡迎一地兩檢","createTime":"2018-09-21T11:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T04:57:17.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"94a0a7ac392ac43b5a695d3020e790384f1fc6c2","tid":830750,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭指香港因高鐵進入「幸福時代」 相信市民會歡迎一地兩檢<br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段即將在周日(23日)通車，行政長官林鄭月娥說，高鐵香港段都對香港有廣泛的重要性，而本港市民能感受「一地兩檢」的方便，相信會得到市民歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥接受內地媒體採訪時說，高鐵香港段雖然只有26公里，但效果非常好，能將香港直接聯繫到國家非常龐大、而且不斷擴展的高鐵網絡，無論是經濟發展還是改善民生，都對香港有廣泛的重要性。她舉例指，未來如果經常要到深圳與深圳市領導開會，乘坐高鐵香港段會非常方便，從西九龍總站到深圳福田，只需十多分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n她強調如果沒有一地兩檢，高鐵的好處就不能發揮，又指享受高鐵紅利的香港市民也將邁入「幸福時代」。高鐵香港段歷時8年興建，最大挑戰是成功落實「一地兩檢」通關程序，她相信高鐵開通後，香港市民能夠感受「一地兩檢」的方便，相信市民會很歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭認為，跨境基建佈局非常完善，有利於提升粵港澳大灣區的人流、物流、資金及資訊流通，通過基建的聯繫，有利香港融入國家發展大局。她有信心通過特區政府與國家鐵總簽署的備忘錄，可以將高鐵香港段做好，即使營運過程出現問題，特區政府與鐵總也可以協商溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-09/21/29687.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2018-09%2F21%2F29687.html&d=X2mAhVlg6XDRO7%2FRs9GaQW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fb044456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-09/21/29687.html</a>"},{"pid":"844b977e9b844d2c63a76bc16d70918878578f2c","tid":830750,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:23:30.000Z","msg":"越講越誇張，<br />\n請問高鐵有幾幸福？"},{"pid":"cba6b069cb2b225ffcc51b75e0cf29bc1ef7fe7d","tid":830750,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"河蟹時代"},{"pid":"ce6a2a7cc839a539dafc26e738eea02c60ea8cb6","tid":830750,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c2d8f4e0f2d9a49c105df686d7309804c77953","tid":830750,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"又咪係條行得快啲嘅直通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e6eaf153fae993823fff264f6cc7caef1349a9","tid":830750,"uid":193642,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"好有北韓味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a6ac7ab7ff9bb1dc5d4cd0b213587421b278c3","tid":830750,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8248fa86f2cc06884cb443265633d2787e43b16f","tid":830750,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"我係西環返工，都唔覺西港島線通車會帶來幸福，最多係方便左<br />\n<br />\n升格到話帶來幸福，真係傻左"},{"pid":"ceefd8545a988a971db67f974003d74c32a6bf77","tid":830750,"uid":41477,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"一世不入高鐵九西站"},{"pid":"9777eb5580be9616dab547fb878c02ceac288700","tid":830750,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"320f56a6466c09b3c39e489a609e4a60b29a6c58","tid":830750,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"上哂天堂，超幸福"},{"pid":"0d2195f8ebfbfb92eecc1cae70d71dc7a81006b6","tid":830750,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8248fa86f2cc06884cb443265633d2787e43b16f","tid":830750,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"我係西環返工，都唔覺西港島線通車會帶來幸福，最多係方便左<br />\n<br />\n升格到話帶來幸福，真係傻左"},"citedBy":0